<ab facs="#facs_489_r1l23">der <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> ſcheden <expan>geweſ<ex>en</ex></expan> ſeyn benennet habt etc / das <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> wır </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_489_r1l24">wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> / VVellen nu dıeſelben ʒwen knecht hıeʒwıſchen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_489_r1l25">ſand Barthlomes tag ſchıerıſt ʒu vns <expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan> . ſo ſüllen ſıe ʒu </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_489_r1l26">vnd von vns für vns vnd dıe <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> on <expan>geu<ex>er</ex>de</expan> vıer tag geleyt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_489_r1l27">haben / vnd mugen ſıe denn mıt ırem rechten vor vns beweıſen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_489_r1l28">daʒ ſıe alſo vnwıſſend vnd vngeuerlıch ʒu der <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> ſcheden </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_489_r1l29"><expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan> ſınd vnd daʒ Jn dauon nıht ʒu Peẅt <expan>word<ex>en</ex></expan> ſey . ſo </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_489_r1l30">wellen wır vns des vmb <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>n</expan> wıllen von Jn <expan>genüge<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>laſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_489_line_1592198959741_808">Denn wo wır eẅch lıeb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dıenſt etc <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut <expan>ſ<ex>upra</ex></expan> </ab>
